<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٢ - <span class="c2">(٢١٩٩)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَاهُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4316">عُثْمَانُ بْنُ أَبِي شَيْبَةَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1132">جَرِيرٌ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ مِثْلَهُ .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>